######################
# JORAM Installation #
######################

A proper Ant environment is needed to compile JORAM:
see <http://jakarta.apache.org/ant/manual/install.html>.

In the src/ directory, type:
 $ ant -projecthelp
to have a list of the available Ant targets for JORAM.

 $ ant
will create a new shipment of JORAM with all the needed libraries
in ship/lib/ (the corresponding target is ship.joram)

 $ ant javadoc
to generate Javadoc

 $ ant clean
to clean all generated files

###########################
# JORAM Samples and Demos #
###########################

You can find samples of JORAM in the samples/ directory.
See samples/src/README for more information.
